\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43744,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/30\/greatest-ten-days\/","url_meta":{"origin":26765,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dhul-Hijjah: Greatest ten days of all time","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best days in the world are the ten days of the month of Dhul-Hijjah.\u201d Source: al-Ama\u0304li\u0304 al-Khami\u0304si\u0304yah li-Shajarii\u0304 1687 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6107,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/09\/these-are-best-ten-days\/","url_meta":{"origin":26765,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhul-Hijjah: These ten days are greatest to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are no days greater and more beloved to Allah than these ten days of Dhul Hijjah, so increase in them your declaration of the oneness of Allah, your exaltation of Him, and your praise of Him.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34328,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/07\/25\/dhul-hijjah-ten-days-most-pure\/","url_meta":{"origin":26765,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Dhul-Hijjah: These ten days most pure to Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 25, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo deeds are more pure to Allah Almighty, nor greater in reward, than good deeds performed in the ten days of the month of sacrificing.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 1774 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33081,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/03\/said-dhull-hijjah-great-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":26765,"position":5},"title":"Sa\u2019id on Dhul-Hijjah: Great striving in first ten days","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Qasim ibn Abi Ayyub reported: When Sa\u2019id ibn Jubayr, may Allah be pleased with him, reached the first ten days of Dhul-Hijjah, he would exert himself in worship so greatly that he would nearly overwhelm himself. Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304rimi\u0304 1815 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0633\u0650\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26765","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=26765"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/26765\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=26765"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=26765"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=26765"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}